a freat video. I love it. I have not exercised since I was 14 years old. I loved to run, dance, basketball, any sport but one day I had an asthma attack doing sports and since then I don't do any exercise. I feel it in the strength in my legs and arms, in my back. I have a lot of back pain and hyperlordosis, but now I am afraid to play sports, I have contractures just by looking at myself, it is a Spanish saying. And I don't have money for a personal trainer or one to one pilates or yoga classes. I have everything at home to do it but I am so afraid that I never do. And deep down I miss it. I hope one day I can do it again.
